# 🎨 SOI Art Director Master Rules

## Core Visual Identity System

### Brand Color Palette
```css
/* PRIMARY SOI COLORS */
--soi-navy: #1e3a5f;        /* Trust, Authority, Headers */
--soi-purple: #8B5C9E;      /* Expertise, Existing Brand */
--soi-pink: #d4a5b8;        /* Care, Human Connection */
--soi-mint: #a8c4a2;        /* Wellness, Recovery */
--soi-white: #ffffff;       /* Clarity, Clean Space */

/* SEMANTIC COLORS */
--primary: var(--soi-navy);
--secondary: var(--soi-purple);
--accent-care: var(--soi-pink);
--accent-wellness: var(--soi-mint);
--surface: var(--soi-white);
```

### Color Usage Hierarchy
1. **Navy (#1e3a5f)**: Navigation, headers, primary CTAs, authority elements
2. **Purple (#8B5C9E)**: Existing brand elements, expertise sections, secondary CTAs
3. **Pink (#d4a5b8)**: Patient care, testimonials, human connection elements
4. **Mint (#a8c4a2)**: Success stories, recovery, wellness outcomes
5. **White (#ffffff)**: Backgrounds, clean spaces, text contrast

## Mandatory Accessibility Standards

### Text Contrast Requirements
- **Minimum**: 4.5:1 contrast ratio for normal text
- **Target**: 7:1 contrast ratio for optimal readability
- **Large Text**: 3:1 minimum (18pt+ or 14pt+ bold)
- **Interactive Elements**: 3:1 minimum for focus indicators

### Approved Text/Background Combinations
```css
/* ✅ SAFE COMBINATIONS */
.text-on-white { color: #1e3a5f; }      /* Navy on White: 12.6:1 */
.text-on-navy { color: #ffffff; }        /* White on Navy: 12.6:1 */
.text-purple-on-white { color: #8B5C9E; } /* Purple on White: 6.2:1 */
.text-on-light-pink { color: #1e3a5f; }  /* Navy on Light Pink tint */
.text-on-light-mint { color: #1e3a5f; }  /* Navy on Light Mint tint */

/* ⚠️ USE WITH CAUTION */
.accent-pink { color: #d4a5b8; }         /* Pink: Only on dark backgrounds */
.accent-mint { color: #a8c4a2; }         /* Mint: Only on dark backgrounds */
```

## Component Color Standards

### Buttons
```css
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--soi-navy);
  color: var(--soi-white);
  border: 2px solid var(--soi-pink);
}

.btn-secondary {
  background: var(--soi-purple);
  color: var(--soi-white);
  border: 2px solid var(--soi-mint);
}

.btn-care {
  background: var(--soi-pink);
  color: var(--soi-navy);
  border: 2px solid var(--soi-navy);
}
```

### Cards & Sections
- **Service Cards**: White background, Navy headers, Purple accents
- **Testimonial Cards**: Light pink tint background, Navy text
- **Procedure Cards**: White background, Purple borders, Navy content
- **Success Stories**: Light mint tint background, Navy text

